---
title: Heirloom Tomato Flatbread with Prosciutto and Pesto
description: It’s hard to go wrong with fresh mozzarella, vibrant tomatoes, and crispy prosciutto. We let these ingredients take center stage in our simple flatbread recipe. If you’re making it in advance, let the dough come to room temperature ahead of time - it’ll be so much easier to roll out!
